  SETUP
    cp 01_BOT/.env.example 01_BOT/.env
    npm run setup

  RUN
    npm run dev

  VERIFY
    npm run check
    npm run test

  BOT
    01_BOT  … discord.js runtime, replies to all non-bot messages, keeps per-scope sessions

  EXTENSIONS
    persona … loads extension-local PERSONA file into pi system prompt

  SKILLS
    (none)

  LINKS
